title: YMCA Celebrates Champions Dinner
text:
Caption YMCA Celebrates Champions Dinner Nick Caito, Special to the Courant Nick Caito, Special to the Courant YMCA Celebrates Champions Dinner Nick Caito, Special to the Courant Nick Caito, Special to the Courant See more galleries The YMCA Celebrates Champions Dinner was held Thursday night at the Connecticut Convention Center. The event raised money for the Read To Succeed adult literacy program as well as other YMCA programs.
Three local community leaders were honored, and the event featured a special appearance by soccer star Mia Hamm.
